 docker.io | docker,
 docker-compose-plugin | docker-compose
Description: manage s-ui deployments with Docker Compose
 SUI-Control installs, configures and maintains an s-ui deployment
 with Docker Compose. Supports ACME (Let's Encrypt) and self-signed
 certificates, multiple init systems (systemd, OpenRC, runit, s6,
 dinit), and runs under a dedicated non-root system user.
